    Megatron turned to Terrorsaur and smiled, "Well, im going to need someone 
who is as a good a leader as I am.....but, we had better get started. Place 
Inferno in the Medical station on the far right of the cave. THis procedure 
wil ltake some time...." Megatron said as he looked at the radar one more 
time. His enemies were gathering at the old cave. Sooner or later they were 
going to find him, bit with the base defences, they would have a fighting 
chance.

    Hell Beast had a large scar on the left of his face where the blast hit 
him. Gremlin lept up and knocked the Fuzor away. "Well, it looks like you 
grew a back bone while I was gone!" Hell Beast hissed.
    "Hell Beast, Im the Commander here, not you!" Aracnia reiterated once 
agian, this time with dominance in her voice. "Besides Im pregnant. I hate 
for it to come out this way, but you hitting me is going to help the phetus 
within me."
